    <pre>After much searching and asking, it appears this is the correct link for adding 
a project (not via adding a bug tracker):
<a href="http://openhatch.org/+portfolio/editor/">http://openhatch.org/+portfolio/editor/</a>

We should at the very least have this linked here:
<a href="http://openhatch.org/search/">http://openhatch.org/search/</a>

and here:
<a href="http://openhatch.org/guide/">http://openhatch.org/guide/</a>

(That latter is where you go when you click "add your project" from the main 
page.)</pre>
